Project Name

AI Restaurant Ordering Website Using Flask + Gemini + Voiceflow + Replit

1. What is System Architecture?

System Architecture is the overall blueprint of an application.

It shows:

All technologies used
How they communicate
Data flow
User interaction
Backend processing
AI integration

Think of it as the master plan of the entire project.

2. Why Do We Need System Architecture?

Imagine building a restaurant without a plan.

Problems:

Kitchen in the wrong place
Billing counter missing
Dining area too small
Customers confused

Similarly,

Building software without architecture causes:

Confusing code
Difficult debugging
Poor scalability
Hard maintenance
